Get the backend function

get_backend_fct.Rd

Get the backend function

Usage

get_backend_fct(backend_type)

Arguments

backend_type

The type of the backend, by default it is connector_fs or connector_db

Value

The backend function

Examples

get_backend_fct("connector_fs")
